---
layout: layout.njk
title: Skills 分类
navSection: skills
description: 按分类浏览 Agent Skills，便于开发者快速找到所需能力。
permalink: categories/index.html
---

<script>document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() { window.location.replace("/#/skills"); });</script>
<section class="nav-layout nav-layout--skills">
  {% set navVariant = "skills" %}
  {% set firstColumnHtml %}
  {% for parent in skillsIndex.categoryTreeWithCounts %}
  <a href="/categories/{{ parent.slug }}/" class="skills-category-tab list-first-item {% if loop.first %}is-active{% endif %}" role="tab">{{ parent.nameZh or parent.name }}</a>
  {% endfor %}
  {% endset %}
  {% set secondColumnHtml %}
  {% set firstParent = skillsIndex.categoryTreeWithCounts[0] %}
  <ul class="list-second-list" id="skills-children-list">
    {% for child in firstParent.children %}
    <li>
      <a href="/categories/{{ child.fullSlug }}/" class="skills-child-link list-second-item">{{ child.nameZh or child.name }}</a>
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
  {% endset %}
  {% include "nav-left-aside.njk" %}
  <div class="nav-content">
    <h1 class="nav-page-title">按分类浏览</h1>
    <p class="nav-page-desc">按使用场景浏览技能，便于快速找到所需能力。同一技能可能属于多个分类。请从左侧选择分类。</p>
  </div>
</section>
